{"tid":486231,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"2017-18 LIHKG香港超級女神聯賽第十四輪投選專區","createTime":"2017-12-01T15:59:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-02T16:22:10.000Z","uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"934a16907b54065ddefa0e9f8d7e15a37ee83278","tid":486231,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T15:59:30.000Z","msg":"以下為即將舉行之賽事<br />\n會員可留意稍後時間發出的比賽專用回覆並以回覆評分功能進行投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(唔識點樣用回覆評分功能黎投票既巴打可以參考下面既教學)<br />\n<br />\n由首場12:00am開始,每兩分鐘開賽一場<br />\n<br />\n陳穎欣@SGv簡淑兒<br />\n李靜儀@SGv李佳芯<br />\n謝安琪v陳嘉倩<br />\n馮盈盈v倪晨曦<br />\n朱千雪v麥明詩<br />\n陳瀅v趙慧珊@SG<br />\n杜小喬v林嘉欣<br />\n張曦雯v苟芸慧<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/hiNda68.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhiNda68.png&h=d4221617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/s2sfX8L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fs2sfX8L.png&h=b53ffa65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n超聯第十三輪積分榜<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yvb3kPg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fyvb3kPg.png&h=4d28c013&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/fg4vwe7.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Ffg4vwe7.png&d=j5%2B4f%2FOYAeE0ffvFxM8fmS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=d5f2ab49\" target=\"_blank\">http://i.imgur.com/fg4vwe7.png</a><br />\n有關主場指定額外得分情況,請參閱主場額外分數增幅表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b20cb6aed1498c5a0081240c1f79fba711b5e5f","tid":486231,"uid":92376,"like":42,"dislike":8,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T15:59:59.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-18 LIHKG香港超級女神聯賽第十四輪</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">*括號內數字為聯賽排名</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-12-2 12am-10pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/p6xJa4y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fp6xJa4y.png&h=4b0c0bc9&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/5nH61zP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5nH61zP.png&h=74f3a7d9&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(12)陳穎欣@SGvs簡淑兒(16)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">聯賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">主場女神票數達到15者會按得票相關情況獲得指定額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"1fd4576ab9049cea73368c8971e5057ad8c468cb","tid":486231,"uid":92376,"like":11,"dislike":52,"score":-41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T16:02:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-12-2 12:02am-10:02pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/DRHkpfm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FDRHkpfm.png&h=083eaa4a&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Dnsh6ug.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FDnsh6ug.png&h=fe8d1f0e&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(8)李靜儀@SGvs李佳芯(2)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">聯賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">主場女神票數達到15者會按得票相關情況獲得指定額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"42b0a1efe3f8abd06de38965d7a07692292cce40","tid":486231,"uid":92376,"like":42,"dislike":21,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T16:04:00.000Z","msg":"<